Workitu Ayanu Gurmu (amụrụ na 19 Eprel na afọ1987, na Addis Ababa) bụ onye Ethiopia na-agba ọsọ nke mita 5000.
Workitu malitere ọrụ ya na agbụrụ ndị na-eto eto na IAAF World Cross Country Championships, na-emecha nke anọ na agbụrụ ụmụ nwanyị na afọ 2004 ma na-emechi nke isii na mbipụta nke 2005 na 2006

Ọ malitere ịgba ọsọ n'ọsọ okporo ụzọ n'afọ 2008 wee merie Egmond Half Marathon n'afọ 2009; oge ya nke 1:16:33 zuru iji merie Hilda Kibet ruo n'ọgwụgwụ. Ọ sonyere na IAAF World Half Marathon Championships na nke mbụ ya na 2009, wee mechie na 14th n'ozuzu
Ọ gbara ọsọ marathon nke onwe ya nke 2:29:25 na 2010 Paris Marathon, na-agwụ na nke ise.
Dị ka a kagbuola mbipụta nke afọ 2010, ọ gbalịrị ịgbachitere aha ya na 2011 Egmond Half Marathon

Ọ bịara nso emeghachi ihe omume ahụ mana ọ mechara bụrụ onye nke abụọ, sekọnd atọ n'azụ onye Ethiopia ibe ya Abebech Afework. Ọ nọ nso na nke kachasị mma na 2011 Rome City Marathon, na-edekọ oge nke 2:29:37, nke wetara ya ọnọdụ nke isii n'ozuzu.
